Bitfinex,is,a,bitcoin,trading,platform,that,provides,users,with,bitcoin,wallets,and,storage,margin,trading,and,liquidity,provisions,The,Bitfinex,API,allows,users,to,access,the,full,functionality,of,the,Bitfinex,platform,including,the,orderbook,the,personal,account,data,and,other,attributes,The,API,uses,REST,calls,and,returns,JSON,An,account,is,required,with,service,and,both,SSL,and,an,API,key,are,used,for,security